social_posts.post_text: ✨Sky above, earth below, fire within✨

✨Circle of Protection✨
The promise to always keep each other safe. The circle is always there, never broken.

✨Spirit Animal✨ 
Always with you. Holding a light and protection. But only if you listen.

✨Spread my dust here✨
When I see such a sacred place, my body absorbs it. 
A coyote walked by as we did this sunset shoot. I didn’t realize then what it meant.

✨Set your soul on fire at sunrise✨
This sunrise hike a few years ago was a little bit magic. @strength.of.spirit and I manifested our new creative lives. It came true ✨✨🌙
⚡️I died a thousand times⚡️

✨What does it mean to be a nature witch?✨
I'm currently listening to the book “The Nature of Witches”(a New York Times best seller)✨ by Rachel Griffin @timesnewrachel -and she describes this as I have always pictured in this beautifully written lfiction masterpiece. 
Precisely what I was thinking about when I made these images of @calah._ in the snow ✨✨✨
I’m so lucky I got to photograph Rachel. I’ll pop the link to the shoot with her in my bio.

✨Water Witch✨
What you can’t see in this image is the snow all over the ground (last shoot) This brave soul got in an icy lake for art, and I salute you. Also I want to print this and hang it at my house, sell prints of this one. It’s very special to me🌹

✨I left my heart in Iceland✨
And I need to go back and get it….

✨Water, Air, Clouds,Spirit✨
Is there nothing like floating through space and time? To be everywhere and nowhere.

Hello @timesnewrachel 
New York Times best seller of the book “The Nature of Witches” and author of “Wild is the Witch” is coming out with a new book 8/2023 “Bring Me Your Midnight” 
Lovely witch, this one❤️ I blogged about this shoot, link in bio.

✨Wandering Wolf Woman✨
I’ve always thought of myself as a lone wolf. I have to wonder what that may be blocking me from….

✨Fight Like Gods✨
I’m so excited you guys! My much needed new website is almost finished! I’m creating a witchy email list too, em me if you want to be on it⚡️

✨Blessed Yule✨
Let the celebrations begin my friends. Rest and embrace new beginnings.

✨Solstice Witch✨
One with nature, comfortable in your skin, in touch with the seasons and the earth. Honors the moon. 
What season do you witch the strongest?

✨Remembering✨
As I look back on my life, everything leads to here for me, creating in nature. It’s where I can always land. 
I can’t believe this year is coming to an end. Time turned into a weird thing during the pandemic, it all seemed like forever and also only a day. 
I’m excited to see what manifestations next year brings for you and for me✨

✨Happy Birthday Witch✨
I’m so proud of you for all you are becoming. I will forever cherish this first day we ever hung out, a 6 hour hike👌🏼⚡️✨

✨You deserve to be seen✨
I didn’t know Crystal Rozy well. I wish I knew her more. Our love of motorcycles brought us together on Instagram, and then we discovered we had a lot more in common -like living in the same neighborhood, loving nature, vegan food, we both fed the birds. The same man worked on both of our bikes. We had the same bike. When I read about her battle with breast cancer, she inspired me so much to be grateful for every day. She won that battle but the cancer returned to her brain. When she updated that she decided to stop treatments and start the hospice process, my heart sank. But it also soared knowing she would be flying free from pain soon, and that she got to make the transition surrounded by those who love her. 
And by a window, at her request.
I think of you daily Crystal- you are now the clouds, the moon, the trees, the earth. I’m lucky to have spent this slice of time with you❤️

✨Light a candle for the New Year✨
Last year was one of my favorite years for my art yet. I’m excited to see what next year brings✨

⚡️Hell Of A Year⚡️
I couldn’t fit it all -and I made it so long nobody will make it through. 
But it’s my diary. I’m super proud of all I’ve become this last year. I’m working my ass off and living my best creative life. 
Wishing you the very best 2023.
✨Ancient Moons, lend me power. Bring me peace and strength this hour. The winds of change upon my skin. Dear luck be mine, let me win✨

✨Feel The Darkness✨
Images like this are best on a big screen. But if you could see closer, alas! It’s a man. A very talented one to say the least. He became a piece of art with me.

✨Wolf Moon✨
Welcome the first full moon of the new year! 
I’m charging my jars of water, sigils, and crystals, journaling like mad, and getting ready to burn all  that weighs weighs me down tonight, down into the ground. 
What are your rituals?

✨Even when I’m dead, I’ll swim through the Earth, like a mermaid of the soil just to be next to your bones✨-Jeffrey McDaniel
Check out this spooky styled ghostly couple’s shoot on the blog. Link in bio baby.

✨It’s trips like these that make me realize my dreams✨
Chipping away and fighting to live a completely free and creative life as an artist. I’ll never give up no matter how hard it can be. #realizeyourdreams

✨To create is to make something that has never existed before. There’s nothing more vulnerable than that✨
I remember when I used to be scared to post my images for fear no one would like them after I worked so hard to make them. None of my friends would comment and it hurt a little. I would run away with my tail between my legs, feeling so vulnerable and unseen. 
Now I realize that is the toxicity of instagram- in its effect it can have on you. Not a reflection of your work. If you are an artist and in that space, in a time when Instagram makes it harder than ever- KEEP GOING! Continue creating until you burst through to a place where nothing can stop you or slow you down, because it becomes as important as the air you breath. 
🙏🏻thanks for being here🙏🏻

✨Spirit Abandoned✨
This shoot was so much fun. Jared @jaredviolin was visiting from Florida -and on this day he experienced full PNW at it’s finest. Climbing a mountain, standing on a cliff(something he had never done) and standing in the water in the rain. 
Jared is an amazing violinist and avid motorcyclist, and this is his love @eros.moto -a bad ass motorcycle mamma (Among many other things) That’s how I met her, the moto community. 
I’m full of gratitude for this day and this story we made-both real and fantasy ✨✨

✨Scale of dragon, tooth of wolf, Witches’ mummy, maw and gulf,
Of the raven’d salt sea shark,
Root of hemlock digg’d I the dark✨Double Double toil and trouble, fire burn and cauldron bubble✨
-Thank you Shakespeare 

This is what happens when witches have me over.

✨Acknowledging the good that you already have in your life is the foundation of abundance✨

Eckhart Tolle

✨Coming Of Age✨
Is there a better term than “senior photos” (I know there is) I’m to come up with a better way to say this on my website. Ideas? 
Also, this is the coolest human. We had so much fun creating together. It was so windy it nearly blew me off my feet. Listening to all the cool things Dillan is into at such a young age was inspiring.

✨The History Of Religion✨
I just binged ‘Vikings Valhalla’ season two. It’s so mind boggling that the Vikings were so split when so many of them either found Christianity or were made to convert. I know it’s just an (f’ing awesome) show- but it still baffles me how so many people were killed if they didn’t convert, if they were given the chance. I mean that goes on both sides. And that seed of hatred runs so deep and far in the world and still exists. I guess I’m always a hippie at heart, and I say worship whoever you wish.
I will say I’m always rooting for the Pagans though. Anyway, loved the show- @samcorlett is amazing!

✨Metamorphose✨
This is one of my favorite shoots of last year with this very talented actress @sanaeloutsis - and I finally got around to putting it on the blog. 
Check it out! ⛓link in bio⛓

✨Dear Universe✨
Thank you for this creative life I’ve carved out for myself. Although some days it feels like a fight, I’m doing the thing I was born to do. I wish that for everyone, to find their purpose. I know that I’m still finding the deeper meanings of my own. I’ll never stop searching, connecting, working, resting, feeling, being, listening and watching in awe of the magic you bring. I will stay in this place of gratitude, the foundation of all abundance (thank you Eckhart) each and every day, as much as I can. 
More magic awaits me. 
(And all of you!)
-Journaling through a few hard days. Love, Me.

✨Connecting with your Guides✨
Lately I’ve been asking them to clear anything that’s blocking me from my manifestations -and to turn up my psychic dial. 
And watching it happen in my mind. 
My guess is micro-dosing🍄 helps heal your subconscious mind, anyone else?

✨Healing Energy✨
I was just chatting with this beautiful soul @motherlinemagic and she was talking about how having a photo session can clear your energy by opening something up for people. Seeing yourself in a new beautiful way may just open a door. As a doula who works with energetics, she recommends people have a magical photo session (not just by me:) 
I believe that any act of self care can open you up for your manifestations big or small. Weather you take a forest walk, visit an animal sanctuary, or get a massage, visualize your dreams. 
And may they come to light. 
I usually post in the morning but I’m spontaneously thinking out loud. Thanks for being here.

✨Beasts of England, Beasts of Ireland, Beasts of every land and clime, hearken well and spread my tidings -
Of the golden future time✨

-George Orwell, Animal Farm

✨Hoh Rainforest✨
The magic of it is on my mind so much I’m heading back there tomorrow for more!

✨Daughter of Sorrow✨
This shoot was so epic, and the house fell soon after, sadly. 
I’m so excited to be making a print shop and this one will be on it.

✨Life grows from death✨
In the Hoh Rainforest. It felt like a faerie or a Yeti could show up at any minute.....

✨”She will share her breath with us when we feel we have lost ours. She will warm us when we are too cold, and cool us down when we are too hot- in emotion, in spirit, in mind, in ideation, in desire, in judgement, in the creative life of the soul. She tells us to be gentle, be brave, but never tame.”✨
Blessed Mother’s Immaculate Love for the Wild Soul - Clarissa Pinkola Estes

✨Akashic Record Crypt✨
This topic has come up three times now, I need to dig in. Anyone had theirs done?

social_posts.post_text:
✨Take Me To Your Master✨
This was such a therapeutic day. What’s a day of shooting like this look like? 
I woke up at 5:30 and left my house at 7:30 am after packing up food for the day, my dogs supplies, too many dresses and props, camera gear, coffees and hot tea. I knew there would be nothing out there. First stop was in 3 hours, final destination 4 hours away. 
We started driving and the rain started to fall. Fuck I forgot my coat! FOR REAL? How? I remembered the twisty stick, the dog treats. And left my coat right by the door. So lame. I laughed. I was pretty bundled up, I figured I’ll power through. 
I was meeting @motherlinemagic at Lake Quinault. She had an extra coat! 
We hiked around and chatted about the deeper things in life. We stopped by a tree for a few photos, which meant she had to change. 
The next stop, Hall Of Mosses (pictured here) was majestic! We shot in there for a quick hour, but I could have shot forever. This place was otherworldly. It would be dark soon. Four hours home, 9:30 pm. I couldn’t believe I left 14 hours ago. It went by so fast. All in a days work, for friendship, adventure, nature and art therapy, so very worth it.

✨Into The Unknown✨
Being at ease and letting go is crucial for the universe to respond to what your asking. Relinquish your attachment to the known, and the mystery becomes irresistible.

✨Beloved✨
I made this image with a beautiful woman/musician. When I look it it I see a woman who rose out of the ashes holding something that she loved very much that was taken from her. A beautiful creature….while the planet fumes in the distance forever beyond. 
Earth witch, I feel your pain.

✨In dreams they come✨
Currently listening to a podcast about dreams on @ologies - I’m looking for a new podcast. I listen to manifestation, health, and all things witchy podcasts. Currently made my way through @spookedpod ✌🏼
Whatcha got for me?

✨Celebrate the return to light✨
Dreams you've created over the dark cold nights are now being lit by the flames of Midwinter.

✨Hello✨
If you don’t know who I am - let me introduce myself again.
First, this owl is the companion of @thefalc0ner. He loves and treats his birds with respect. I believe he was a bird in another life. 
Maybe I was too. 
I’m Dawndra. I’ve been taking photos for 20 years or more, but some of those years I was lost, so in many ways I feel like I had a new beginning 6 years ago when I quit drinking. I’m high energy, completely goofy, always interested in the magical, daydreaming, motorcycle loving, dog and cat and plant mom, happily single, mother of my art. Usually I’m in jeans and a hoodie. 
I wake up every day to yoga and writing, burning and ritual, then I head to a forest with my dog Ezme. This morning ritual is super important to me. 
I love to travel, I love netting new people although I’m terrible at going out lately. I often blast heavy metal, or Stevie Nicks, or mellow witchy sounds, or crystal bowls. I edit my days away listening to books and podcasts. I’m in my late 40’s and owning it. I donate to animal sanctuaries. I do what I can for the animals. Episode 3 of ‘The Last of Us’ just rocked my world. I have a brother Derrick, he’s a heavy metal drummer. I lost my mom 10 years ago. I have another photo page @portraitsbydawndra 
That’s a lot of rambling - but I want to know about you!

✨What do I bring to my photo shoots?✨
The list could look like all or a few of these items, depending on if I’m able to bring a cart or just carry a bag. Skull, lantern, rope, candles, candle holders, mask, dresses, smoke, a prism and other things to shoot through like fabric, fabric to drape, bones, sage, crystals for luck, mirror brush touch up stuff, camera and extra lens, light and stand. Sometimes add motorcycle. Hopefully always my dog. 
Water. 
I could use an assistant🔥✌🏼

✨Full Moon In Leo✨
Secrets that have been buried deep may be revealed, the energy frenetic. Skeletons come out of the closet. 
Relationships may shift. Don’t be afraid of change. 
Breakdowns may lead to breakthrough.

Thank you for making this moving image with me @minniesarah79 ✨you are beautiful inside and out.

✨There is nothing more important to true growth than realizing that you are not the voice of the mind- you are the one who hears it✨
Loving “The Untethered Soul” by Micheal Singer
✨Find Your Wild✨

✨Year if the Water Rabbit✨
True story, I met this young rabbit woman walking through the park. She had an accordion, her adorable dog, and an armload of firewood. She told me it was for Imbolc. I decided I must photograph her immediately, and it was a joy.

✨Inside the Joshua Tree✨
I made a little blog about what we were thinking about while we were there. 
Lately I have been revisiting some old images/shoots and reworking them with my new brain. 
And if you want to get 2 blogs a month, short and sweet- subscribe to my newsletter.
⛓️Link in bio⛓️
Thanks loves❤️✌🏼

✨Since the day she was brought into this world, it was known. This one is something special✨
@motherlinemagic

✨I have met the witches of Taos. And they are magic✨
If you could live anywhere besides where you live now, all reality aside, nothing holding you back…where would you be?

✨Dark Night of the Soul✨
Have you been through one? Did you come out a different person?Big changes are coming, the answers are always in the shadows.

✨I am open and ready to receive✨
Mantra for today. Feeling grateful for this creative life I live, and I’m ready to uplevel.

✨Circle of Protection✨
I like doing little protection spells before I take big trips or ride my motorcycle. I envision white, silver, gold light beams circling me. I even send the beams around my dog and cat. 
If anyone has any fun spells or mantras for protection, do share!

✨Light Witch Becomes Shadow Witch✨
From gathering herbs and forest delights, to casting spells and chasing demons.
A witch is all powerful, and can choose the light or the darkness.

✨When the men on the chessboard get up and tell you where to go 
And you’ve just had some kind of mushroom, and your mind is moving low 
Go ask Alice, I think she’ll know✨
-Grace Slick
I’ve always loved this song, and I see the world as such a trippy place.

✨Listening is suspending disbelief. Just being in that moment, hearing fully what someone has to say✨
Listening fully might bring out new ideas. I used to be so scattered, unable to be present most of the time. I’ll work on this forever.

✨I have realized that the past and future are real illusions, that they exist in the present, which is what there is and all there is✨Alan Watts
With @sevenlionsmusic and @thefalc0ner

✨Circle of Protection✨
One way of creating this is not to let other people’s fears cast shadows of doubt in what you’re seeking. Identify your resistance. Surround yourself with a positive force. 
Be willing to see the unchangeable change. 
I’m not telling you what to do, I’m just talking to myself as usual ❤️✨

✨The Letter✨
The letter that changed the witch forever, and turned her heart to blackness🖤
You guys -I made my first witchy video! This is something I want to incorporate in my work …and I’m not going to lie, I’ve been putting it off for years. I’m still brand new at this - so it’s not coming out the way I’m imagining quite yet, but I won’t stop working.
If you like it, honor it and share it🙏🏻or just let me know whatcha think!
❤️Goddess knows I could use the encouragement. 
@tabithabastienofficial you are such a darling, I’m proud of all you’ve made in this world-including this.

✨Shoot with me✨Giveaway✨

Hi friends! I’ve been talking about this on my story, and thank you to those who joined my email coven for an early entry. (You can enter again now for a second entry)
I’m giving away a full on photo shoot with me, witchy and ethereal, here in the Seattle area, at the location of my choosing, to be shot in April or May.
I might have something for you to wear, or you may have something, or I can help you find affordable options. 
✨
To enter: tag a friend who you think might like this shoot- AND comment why you want to shoot with me in a few words. 

✨Extra Entry✨join my email list in bio👽then DM me “done!” 

Winner will be announced in the next 2 weeks. 
This shoot can be used for any witch if any size, color, or sex. Or for a maternity witch shoot. 

Thank you! Love and Light Witches!
✨I release you✨

social_posts.post_text:
✨Living in the field of all possibilities✨
I believe that spending quiet time in nature (every day for me) helps us connect with ourselves, or our higher self even. 
Sometimes I take a “wonder walk” 
I walk through the forest and allow myself to dream about anything my heart desires. 
Thank you @motherlinemagic for being such a wonder witch - a witch with big dreams❤️

✨My Life is in Harmony with Cosmic Law. (Om Varunam Namah)✨ -Deepak Chopra 

I’m loving this 21 day abundance meditation with Deepak where every day he explains some beautiful laws of abundance, and gives you a centering thought for the day -along with it’s Sanskrit Mantra, and a lovely meditation. I’m loving it so much, DM me and I’ll send it to you❤️

✨Ghost Ship✨ 
The bones of ship, how it looks so lonely. 
But she will always be there. Wandering for eternity, translucent and barefoot, lost and searching, as long as it’s bones remain.

✨Ritual✨
There are so many rituals we can put our energies into, creating magic with intention. 
My latest favorite is talking to my water, especially new moon water. Have you read Dr Emoto’s book- ‘The Hidden Messages in Water’? I just started it! He shows the direct consequences of destructive thoughts and the thoughts of love and appreciation to the formation of water crystals. Fascinating! 
I love when science is witchy✨Everything is energy.

✨WINNER✨✨✨
First off I want to say - you are all winners!!! Being alive is winning. Breathing, walking, seeing if we’re fortunate enough. 
Anyway…
I put 115 names in my witch hat and the name I pulled out was …. Drum roll……. @timesnewrachel !!!!!🤟🏻🤟🏻🤟🏻
Congrats witchy woman! 

Since I was lucky enough to shoot with Rachel once before her first book came out- I felt like I should choose A SECOND piece of paper from the hat. So yes, a whim, I decided to choose TWO of you - and the second name I pulled is @heather_underground 🐺🐺🐺🐺✨✨✨✨
Hell to the yes my witches! Let’s get to planning your shoots!!

✨Mother and Daughter✨
They walk barefoot while they sing heathen songs to the stars. Dance by the fire in the new moon light. They always look for omens and talk to the wind, and cast protection spells upon the animals and forest where they live. 

I loved this shoot with a woman and her two daughters.

✨Burning✨
So many of our ancestors were burned, enslaved, oppressed. It gets into your being and stays with you weather we know it or not. 
I’ve been on a path to healing for some time now.
The next level for me is to release ancestral trauma and any of my own stubborn trauma that wants to stick around no matter what I do by myself.
Im looking for the mother.

✨Take me away even if only in my mind✨ 
Time spend dreaming is never wasted.
✨Unleash Your Power✨

✨Scripting with the Universe✨
Write down all the things you desire in your life, and be careful what you witch for…
✨Meditation✨Call to the Raven✨

✨That moment you realize that all you want to do in life is to empower woman…. ✨
@iamkellygraham you are a force 🔥
✨Double double, toil and trouble✨

✨Totem Deer✨
Deer are highly sensitive creatures. People with a deer as an animal guide are usually caring and compassionate, and they can calm you with their soothing energy. Deer are aware of the subtle energies happening all around them. 
They are gentle and innocent, and we love it when they share their natural beauty with us. 
Being in tune with your spirit guides can tell you so much about yourself.
Deer= grounding, energy, flow. 
Thank you for last night @motherlinemagic - I feel as though your spirit guide graced me with it's presence.

✨Magic in the Forest✨
Spirit Animals, Mirror Magic, Fire Magic, but mostly sister witches are more powerful when they come together to combine their powers. 
Thank you @eros.moto and @motherlinemagic for creating with me🙏🏻 You are both a gift to this world and the next.
I’m still very new at video so stay tuned my friends.

✨Portrait of A Woman✨
I made this video and image with my #lensbabysol45 

A lot of woman come to me to boost their confidence, or to remind themselves of the beauty inside or out that they know is somewhere waiting to be released. Maybe they are in the middle of shadow work -or derp emotional healing. They have experienced growth as a human, and are proud of the long road it took to get there. 

 Wherever you are, I’m here for it.

Thank you to this beautiful woman @iamkellygraham for sharing your energy with me!

✨Algorithm ✨
Someone told me your not supposed to post on weekends and posting at this time or that is the best. 
The only problem with that is that I don’t give a f✨ck😘
Happy Saturday Witches!
✨The sacred symbol of the Goddess Eostre was a hare✨
✨More Powerful in Numbers✨

✨Fly alongside your shadows✨
Releasing them can open many doors.
✨Dreams, Freedom, Traps, Transformation✨

✨In Flow✨
Sometimes after a shoot I drive away thinking “what the F just happened?!”because I get so into it, so in flow I loose myself. And I’m a giant dork, I like to have fun. It always goes by super fast. 
I’ve shot several times with this woman who’s a beautiful talented musician - she brought her lovely family along for this one. And I felt comfortable enough to ask her to take a quick shot of me with the most magical sacred creatures. 
@thefalc0ner you are always a dream to work with, it’s been too long.

✨Mother Earth✨I am the storm✨
Happy Earth Day. But is our mother happy? What can we do to give back to her? 
I asked her this question as I made this self portrait on sacred land in Taos, NM. 
I am the storm.
✨Drink my poison and I’ll give you my heart✨

✨Ritual✨
Black and White or color friends?

⚡️Love Ritual⚡️

Thank you for sharing your magic with me, and your darkness with each other… and loving one another all the more for it✨✨✨ @eros.moto and @jaredviolin 🔥

✨Heart of Taos✨
Maybe the land speaks louder there because it hasn’t yet been trampled. I heard that the soul of Taos itself will chew you up and spit you out if it doesn’t want you, or wants to test you… to what your made of. The history is loud.

✨Window to the Soul✨
The deeper I go into my work, the more I’m interested in peeking into the soul of whom I work with. It’s storytelling. 
This woman is a single mom and a kitchen witch. She makes tinctures and tonics, and has a beautiful skincare business and she makes amazing organic products that I have been using for years. She does facials (and more) that make you glow for weeks. 
But there’s much more to Nicole than that, more than words. That’s where the images come in. 
It was so great to work with you @westcoastwillowskincare - and an amazing hair and make up witch @seanna_miriah ❤️

✨✨Don’t forget my darling one, you have magic in your bones. In the deep place beyond this world, in the cracks of your bones, lies the blood of your witch mother✨And the blood and bones of her mother. They lie dormant, always watching. Not fully awake, but not gone forever, they are whispering to you. Only to be heard in the silence✨

✨When you touch the earth with your bare skin, the memories penetrate your soul✨
New Mexico

✨Love Buzz✨
I remember the day I found out the song “Love Buzz” from my favorite Nirvana record was a cover song. I still love both versions so much. But the Shocking Blue version is strait up witchy …like this love potion witch @eros.moto ✨✨
✨Tethering Souls✨

✨Witch of the North✨
Thank you darling vegan witch, harm none is a witches creed we have in common. 
Heather drove down from Canada and we had a lovely dinner where we confessed some secrets, and then we had a witchy forest adventure….
Complete with me having a small melt down over losing my lighter to light candles with 🤟🏻and my pug going wild a few times. Oh and kids throwing rocks at us while we shot photos. For real, lots of rocks. 
It was real, it was raw. 
And I love her.

✨Friendship with our death would enable us to celebrate the eternity of the soul witch death cannot touch✨
From this beautiful book I'm reading, - Anam Cara (means soul friend) spiritual wisdom from the Celtic World by John O'Donohue 
Poetic and beautiful book so far.

✨When only you can protect yourself…✨

When fear backs you up against the wall, the only way to go is through it. And it can change you.
✨You’re pulling at my heart strings Cowboy✨

✨What’s in a witches’ heart?✨
With @heather_underground 🙏🏻

✨Invoke Mother Goddess✨
New baby ritual ideas…
White candles, a symbol of protection. A circle of candles symbolizes the cycle of life and protection. Focus on intentions, call upon the deities or spirits and thank them for their protection. Make an offering. Use a small charm or protective amulet. Sprinkle herbs to purify the space. Speak words of affirmation and love to your unborn baby. 
Write your wishes on a special piece of paper. 
I wrote about this shoot on my latest blog. Link in bio🔥
Congrats on your new beautiful baby you guys🌟🌟

✨Self Portrait in The Vortex✨
What makes a Vortex site special? Is it just a fancy woo woo thing to say? 
It depends on how open you are. 
The type of energy in a Vortex is etheric and raises your frequency level. It also creates an easier gateway for beings in other realms if existence to visit our 3D world. The Verde Valley has been utilized for thousands of years as a place of healing and spiritual rejuvenation from native peoples to present day. 
I was called to be barefoot, get in the water, chat with everyone I met, enjoy the sunsets, and to write. The biggest call was to make art- and ride a motorcycle. 
I’ll be spending more time here and I’m excited to see what this energy brings to my artwork. 
Self Portrait, Sedona Arizona. Vortex.

✨The age old sacred relationship between photographers and musicians✨
I LOVE music and I love working with musicians to create art that represents their essence. And when our vibes sink up, it’s just magical. Music needs these images both moving and still to help convey their sound. It’s been happening through the ages. 
I also love that whenever a musician that I follow posts images from a photographer, they (should and mostly do) ALWAYS give the due credit. 
Artists supporting artists, we have to continue to build each other up. 
I’m not afraid to share a photographer or musician that I admire, it’s not a contest, we are in this together. 
Thank you to all of the beautiful musicians that I have had the honor to work with, including this one @ailisanewhallmusic 🙏🏻❤️🙏🏻

✨Energy✨

Here’s a little behind the scenes look at my shoot from yesterday. I never make videos of me working and my excuse is that I have my hands full, my brain is too full👽but it’s an excuse. Thank you for making it @eros.moto 🤟🏻

Here’s  a little info about my process. 

Prep time before I leave (hour to hour and a half) 
Scratch that ***
Prep time- my whole life leading up to this 😆
Shoot time - 2 hours but can go 3. 

Tools - backpack with gear-Nikon D810 with sigma art 35. Sometimes I use my 50. Always take a few shots with my #lensbaby and I love to use a prism. I have a Nikon 85 but only bring sometimes. 

Cart on wheels overflowing with props and lighting, candles, sage, dresses and fabrics. Oh and a dog blanket for Ezme but she prefers my models dress👌🏼

I just got my #smokeninja - a little rad smoke tool that I learned about from artist @vallerina01 (thank you)

Stereo with witchy sounds. 

Peanuts for crow friends. 

Familiar - Ezme the Witchdog 

Fun fact -Sometimes I pee in the woods🌲

Model/Muse/Piece of living art/witch @eros.moto 
I love her to death. 

I love the energy she brings to a shoot and also her gratitude. Don’t shoot a model for fun if they are the type to not even respond to their gallery. Unless you don’t care- or don’t give them the images. That makes sense too. Choose wisely the energy you give out. 

These shoots are my life’s blood. They make my heart beat. I do them sometimes in exchange for money - (info on my website) and sometimes just to keep creating, practicing, learning, growing, and being a weirdo in the woods. 
It’s what I do. 
I can’t breathe without this in my life. 
Thank you for being here! 
Much love❤️‍🔥
Dawndra
